#: routes/splash.py:24
msgid "Never sing again... ever."
msgstr "永遠不要再唱歌了...永遠不要。"

#: routes/splash.py:25
msgid "That was a really good impression of a dying cat!"
msgstr "那真的很像一隻垂死的貓！"

#: routes/splash.py:26
msgid "Thank God it's over."
msgstr "感謝上帝，終於結束了。"

#: routes/splash.py:27
msgid "Pass the mic, please!"
msgstr "請把麥克風傳給下一位！"

#: routes/splash.py:28
msgid "Well, I'm sure you're very good at your day job."
msgstr "嗯，我相信你的正職工作一定很出色。"

#: routes/splash.py:31
msgid "I've seen better."
msgstr "我見過更好的。"

#: routes/splash.py:32
msgid "Ok... just ok."
msgstr "還可以...只是還可以。"

#: routes/splash.py:33
msgid "Not bad for an amateur."
msgstr "對業餘選手來說不錯。"

#: routes/splash.py:34
msgid "You put on a decent show."
msgstr "你表演得不錯。"

#: routes/splash.py:35
msgid "That was... something."
msgstr "那真是...有點特別。"

#: routes/splash.py:38
msgid "Congratulations! That was unbelievable!"
msgstr "恭喜！那真是難以置信！"

#: routes/splash.py:39
msgid "Wow, have you tried auditioning for The Voice?"
msgstr "哇，你有考慮過去參加《好聲音》嗎？"

#: routes/splash.py:40
msgid "Please, sing another one!"
msgstr "請再唱一首！"

#: routes/splash.py:41
msgid "You rock! You know that?!"
msgstr "你太棒了！你知道嗎？！"

#: routes/splash.py:42
msgid "Woah, who let Freddie Mercury in here?"
msgstr "哇，誰讓佛萊迪·默丘里進來了？"

